# Project: Nail Salon Appointment Scheduler (Cothemaniculator)

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 with App Router
- TypeScript
- Supabase (PostgreSQL database + Auth)
- Tailwind CSS
- Google Calendar API integration (planned)
- Twilio (SMS) + Resend (Email) for notifications (planned)

## Project Structure
- /app - Next.js pages and routes
  - /auth - Authentication (Google OAuth working)
  - /book - Booking flow (in progress)
  - /dashboard - Customer dashboard
- /lib/supabase - Supabase client/server utilities
- /lib/types - TypeScript type definitions
- /components - React components
- /middleware.ts - Auth middleware

## Key Features Implemented
x Google OAuth authentication (working in production)
x Customer management in Supabase
x Complete database schema with conflict prevention
x Deployed to Vercel (https://co-the-maniculator.vercel.app)

## Database Schema
- services: Base services and metadata
- service_length_options: Length pricing for extensions
- nail_art_tiers: 4 tiers of nail art complexity
- customers: User profiles linked to auth
- appointments: Bookings with conflict checking
- appointment_services: Many-to-many relationship
- business_hours: Operating hours with date overrides
- blocked_slots: Manual time blocks
- google_calendar_events: Calendar sync (not yet implemented)

## Business Rules
- 1 hour buffer between ALL appointments (not shown to customers)
- 16 hour minimum advance booking
- 2 month maximum booking window
- Max 4 future appointments per customer
- Nail art is REQUIRED with all services
- Appointments must END by 9pm (not just start before 9pm)
- Double booking prevention via database triggers
- 24 hour cancellation policy

## Services & Pricing
1. Hard Gel Overlay: $50, 90min
2. Hard Gel Extensions: $55-$85 (by length), 150min
3. Polygel Extensions: $60-$100 (by length), 180min
4. Same Product Fill-In: $45, 90min
5. Nail Art Tiers:
   - T1: $10, +30min (French tips, chrome, pearl, single color)
   - T2: $15, +45min (Multiple designs, bloom art, animal prints)
   - T3: $20, +60min (3+ designs, 3D art, hand painted)
   - T4: $30, +90min (4+ designs, encapsulation, junk nails, sculpted)
6. Foreign Removal: $15, +45min
7. My Product Removal: Free, +45min

